Review_Text: SpoilerThe production values are solid and it's an interesting story but why this person?She's a human train wreck, both personally and professionally and one wonders what she has to show us or teach us.It is rare for me to come out of a movie and especially a documentary, feeling that I have learned nothing.

Review_title: Wanita the Queen of Honky Tonk
Review_Text: Loved this documentary, based on Wanita the Queen of Honky Tonk and her quest to record her new album at THE home of country music - NASHVILLE.Even if you don't like country music, the story of Wanita is raw, real and beautiful.
